N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1225.22 - Improperly packaged, marked, leaking or loose freight not accepted for handling

State Regulations

Freight which is not properly packaged and marked, or
is in a leaking or loose condition will not be accepted for
handling. Notes
